<item>
            <title>[LU-12405] Add support for Oracle Linux uek 5r2 kernel</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12405</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Enable building lustre against the Oracle Linux UEK kernels&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add detection for uek kernel signature and suppress warnings about expecting an Ubuntu, RHEL or SLE kernel.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Enable building if Oracle OFED extensions are not suppressed (kernel default is enabled).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Oracle Linux (or CentOS 7) with uek 5r2 kernel 4.14.35-1902.0.18.el7uek</environment>
        <key id="55889">LU-12405</key>
